\alpha = c
c > 0
F(y)=\begin{cases} 0, & y<0\\ \left(\frac{y}{\theta}\right)^\alpha, &0\le y \le \theta \\ 1, ,&y>\theta,\end{cases}
0<k<1
P(k < \frac{Y_{(n)}}{\theta} \le 1) = 1 - k^{cn}.
P(k\theta < Y_{(n)} < \theta) = F_{Y_{(n)}}(\theta) - F_{Y_{(n)}} (k\theta).
